{"tid":946520,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"點解鋼鍊入面愛德華同艾爾一開始人體鍊成之前，唔用昆蟲動物嚟試吓先呢？","createTime":"2018-12-18T14:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T15:17:59.000Z","uid":64694,"like":11,"dislike":170,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"c2c9ac8c08e2e51daba69d76b10ae924968d59bc","tid":946520,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:41:07.000Z","msg":"如果一開始用昆蟲動物嚟試吓先，就算失敗咗代價似乎冇咁大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲人做實驗都要試吓先啦，佢哋點解一嚟就做？同埋點解佢哋唔睇吓書或者睇吓有冇成功例子先呢？如果佢哋一早知失敗咗會搞成咁，佢哋重會唔會噉做呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且佢哋失去咗身體先去研究去搵賢者之石，佢哋點解唔喺人體鍊成之前就去研究一下賢者之石先呢？係因為佢哋嗰陣太細過咩都唔知，而且佢哋阿媽死咗俾呢樣嘢沖昏咗頭腦？定係佢哋見完真理之後先知賢者之石有回復身體嘅用途？"},{"pid":"650fc1d0fbccbc61d578591383008abc5c1c5499","tid":946520,"uid":117934,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1961a7017ac209013cfec2430f0c9bc5702ba42","tid":946520,"uid":151534,"like":129,"dislike":0,"score":129,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:43:59.000Z","msg":"由頭睇過啦"},{"pid":"7a52351182205267d1093a24f61dfdffab9c195e","tid":946520,"uid":128089,"like":210,"dislike":3,"score":207,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:47:16.000Z","msg":"痴線，連鋼鍊撚都開呢D ON9 POST，學火影撚咩。"},{"pid":"a7303582e7057413df4e0bca23fb53235fe33cd0","tid":946520,"uid":128089,"like":131,"dislike":0,"score":131,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:48:09.000Z","msg":"睇返個USER NAME原來又係一件火影傻鳩，唔怪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be7807931fe08112b64453c42114a52e4304615","tid":946520,"uid":4237,"like":259,"dislike":1,"score":258,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:48:52.000Z","msg":"你都識講人體練成啦<br />\n唔係蟲體練成呀<br />\n人體練成陣就係昆你人體練成，練咩蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8284db62eb8235cdfabce9548dc09a068dc640d","tid":946520,"uid":4237,"like